	adhimokkha


'determination', decision, resolve: 
 is one of the mental concomitants (cetasika) and belongs to the group 
of mental formations (sankhāra-kkhandha). 
 In M.111, it is mentioned together with other mental concomitants. 
 See Tab. II, III.

