samvega-vatthu


'the sources of emotion',  
or of a sense of urgency, are 8:  
"birth, old age, disease, death, being 4; the suffering in the lower states 
of existence being the 5th; further, the misery of the past rooted in the cycle 
of rebirth, the misery of the future rooted in the cycle of rebirth, the misery 
of the present rooted in the search after food" (Vis.M. III.).

